16 WHEREAS, the Vikings have brought immense pride to their school and community,
17 earning a reputation for athletic excellence, sportsmanship, and the relentless pursuit of
18 success both on and off the field.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body congratulate the Lowndes County High School baseball team on
21 winning the 2024 GHSA 7A State Baseball Championship and extend best wishes for
22 continued success in their future endeavors.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
24 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
25 Lowndes County High School baseball team.
